data.description:
OWN YOUR OWN LAND!!! This beautifully unique property is fully renovated and upgraded,  Become apart of this beautifully active 55+ community. Stainless steel appliances, large kitchen island surrounded by brand new cabinets, LED lighting throughout, quartz countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms, travertine tiled showers and 100% waterproof luxury vinyl flooring also and an Enclosed tiled air conditioned lanai that could easily be an extra room. 2022 metal roof. This home is very unique and beautifully redone. You also have space to store your boat/rv available in a separate gated area. Washer and dryer room is insulated! Comes with brand new washer and dryer! Everything in this home is new as of august 2022. This community has lots of activities/group’s and events to keep you busy! Minutes from the beaches! Don’t miss out on the ONLY home in this community that’s been completely and fully renovated. It won’t last long. 
(Owner has real estate license)
data.whatILove: We love this house because it’s land owned, and also everything is brand new and updated.
